Try to keep holidays agnostic where possible.

For example:

```jsx
<div>
<h4 className="typography-body-10 text-muted mb-3">FOR EXAMPLE:</h4>
<p className="typography-body-10 mb-2 ml-4"><span className="text-success font-bold">Do:</span> festive season, holiday season</p>
<p className="typography-body-10 mb-2 ml-4"><span className="text-success font-bold">Do:</span> Lunar New Year</p>
<p className="typography-body-10 mb-3 ml-4"><span className="text-danger font-bold">Don't:</span> Chinese New Year</p>
<p className="typography-body-10 text-muted italic">Note: ‘Christmas’ can be used in mass comms but not personalised comms.</p>
</div>
```
